	<aura:description>
        This component loads a map with all legal and prospect accounts associated with the commericalentity in the context. 
        It marks the account with open opportunities in green color and size of the marker is propoprtional to the amount. 
        Accounts with no open opportunities are marked in red color. 
        
        <p>This component can not be used independently. It has to be used with HubEntitiesListcomponent.</p>
    </aura:description>	
</aura:documentation>